## Abstract

I configured two pins as outputs - one of them supports ISP mode (P0_13):
```
DigitalOut p1(P0_13);
DigitalOut p4(P0_16);
```

![iocon](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25270775/33482911-85b54d4e-d69b-11e7-824b-ccb2ef572c63.PNG)


Running this code works fine. Both pins are toggling:
```
